{"tid":1755812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓國戰線]Super Junior各地Fans幫手係ig Twitter 聲援香港!!","createTime":"2019-11-25T18:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T17:13:50.000Z","uid":177905,"like":176,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"3278d134f48429aea5f354dc29093ede11acf0b1","tid":1755812,"uid":177905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事源琴日SuperJunior成員崔始源係Twitter like左韓網有關中槍手足既一篇新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGV0Soz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGV0Soz.jpg&h=1774698f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班大陸小粉紅見到就發曬癲話佢干涉中國內政，要佢道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始源係微博到打左段野 但都冇講明立場 只係話希望世界和平<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UohuLJT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUohuLJT.png&h=1d756191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班大陸閪就痴左線咁叫佢要係twitter同ig道歉（正係係微博講都知咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就退團 微博嘈到好勁<br />\n有啲小粉紅衝出黎要求取消佢係港澳台活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTOmBRd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTOmBRd.png&h=8e995f82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQPXUCT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQPXUCT.jpg&h=85649ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[size=7]<strong>台灣fans覺得好嬲所以發起左係twitter instagram聲援香港活動</strong>[/size=7]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdZMNWL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdZMNWL.png&h=7a0fb79a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcNeWP5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcNeWP5.png&h=5e4a78ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEQ0Sor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEQ0Sor.jpg&h=011d62c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加左#protectsiwon #godblesshongkong 既hashtag</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">所以大家幫手係twitter search #godblesshongkong 瘋狂retweet啊<br />\n台灣外地fans都有幫手post 唔好浪費左始源既好心!!!!!<br />\n唔好比班大陸閪得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界唔係圍住佢地轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"36378785ebb21c859553f672223e82a18568ebc6","tid":1755812,"uid":177905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:33:35.000Z","msg":"Push1"},{"pid":"a55ffcbe55aacb8ead7b4ee626e09e7e3c6c5c5f","tid":1755812,"uid":177905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:33:46.000Z","msg":"Push2"},{"pid":"cbecfe348f2d8c33496c6499068cd8225f2dd9f1","tid":1755812,"uid":177905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"Push3"},{"pid":"f7ec313cfd16de2c70b7d7f5f0a43ada1ba21714","tid":1755812,"uid":177905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"Push4"},{"pid":"2d238225619e73c71f0c17fa25fddd5ff5cdbed4","tid":1755812,"uid":2110,"like":0,